#16900
The Executive Office~
{BLACK}
   As you enter this room the large stone doors swing silently shut 
   behind you.  As you glance about in the dim light you see a 
   large ebony table surrounded with  several soft leather chairs.  
   The room is huge and extends into the horizon.  The walls on 
   either side are shelved with more books than you have ever seen.  
   The  bookshelves extend high into the rafters and walkways 
   extend away at each level.  There are two large gargoyles 
   perched precariously above either side of the stone door.

~
