#16903
{BLUE}The Sailor on the Seas of Fate{blue}~
{CYAN}
   And leaving his cousin Yrkoon sitting as regent upon the 
   Ruby Throne of Melnibone, Elric sailed from Imrryr, the 
   Dreaming City, and went to seek an unknown goal in the 
   worlds of the Young Kingdoms where Meniboneans were, at 
   best, disliked.

   Perhaps if you follow his meandering path you will find him, 
   maby then will you begin to find answers.  Here a ship is 
   docked.  Its design baroque and unfamiliar, with high decks 
   fore and aft, and no evidence or rowing ports.  The mist eddies 
   and more of the red light pours through to illuminate the 
   vessel, revealing the large wheels on both the foredeck and the 
   rear deck, the slender mast with its furled sails, the 
   complicated geometrical carvings of its rails and its figure 
   head, the great, curving prow which gives the ship an 
   impression of power and strength and makes you think that 
   this must be a warship.

