#16904
{WHITE}The Weird of the White Wolf{white}~
{CYAN}
   You frantically walk along a peaceful valley path. At any 
   other time you might have enjoyed this little jaunt through 
   nature, but today your thoughts are heavy with a great burden. 
   The knowledge that it is up to you to maintain that ever fragile 
   balance between Law and Chaos. Through your travels you 
   have discovered that the balance is dangerously close to 
   tipping toward the side of Law. You know that there can only 
   be one cause. The one known as the Dark Lady Myshella, 
   Goddess of Law must be behind it. You have to find her and 
   stop her before the entire balance of the universe tips toward 
   Law. An unbalancing that would eventually cause its complete 
   destruction.

