#16907
{BLUE}On the Ship that Sails Between Worlds{blue}~
{CYAN}
   You are standing on the main deck of the ship.  There is a 
   dark mist that envelops it and the shore is barely discernable.  
   You sense that the mist has at some point become a part of the 
   ship and it follows you as you sail through the seemingly 
   murky sea.  There is a cabin built into the aft deck, while the 
   decks themselves rise up below the billowing sails.  There is a 
   ladder that leads to the rear of the ship.

