#16908
{BLUE}The Large Fore Deck{blue}~
{CYAN}
   As you step up onto the fore deck of this aged vessel you can 
   hear the ship quietly moan as the waves of the sea push 
   against the sides of the hull.  You notice that the ship is 
   impossibly old and the wood seems to have seen a thousand 
   storms at sea.  There is a large figurehead, of which, you can 
   see only a portion of.  Looking over the prow you can see 
   through the thick mist to the horizon, and you think this quite 
   odd.

