#16909
{BLUE}The Captain's Quarters{blue}~
{CYAN}
   This is the captain's private chamber.  The woodwork is 
   intricately carved and oiled.  There are large slanted pane 
   windows which arc in a panoramic view of the deep mist you 
   can see outside of the ship.  There is a large heavy wooden
   bed and several large storage cabinets dispersed throughout 
   the room.  In addition you see a large ancient looking rug 
   which is painstakingly detailed in its depiction of what appear 
   to be dragons mounted with riders.

