#16911
{BLUE}The High Aft Deck{blue}~
{CYAN}
   Since you have been aboard this vessel the sea and the 
   perpetual mist have had much to say.  Of the lost Emperor of 
   Melnibone, of the whereabouts of the runesword 
   Stormbringer, and of the forgotten city of Tanelorn.... the 
   ruins of Tenelorn.  The ancient city of Tenelorn, now home of 
   the beings Agak and Gagak.  The mist tells you that the ruins 
   are to be found upon an island.  And that upon this island, at 
   the heart of the ruins is to be found one whole building.   It is 
   this building which the dread two use.  It is that which you 
   must attack, and slay the pair and their servants.

   You feel the ship sway slightly and perhaps feel the coming of 
   the storm.  In the center of the deck there is a large wheel,  
   which, with the guidance of the mist may lead you to 
   Tanelorn... and the home of the pair.

