{BLUE}The Ruins of Tanelorn{blue}~
{CYAN}
   At times, as you advance cautiously inland, a peculiar 
   flickering light sometimes crosses the island so that the 
   outlines of the place become unsteady before returning to 
   focus.  It could be that these are shadows cast by objects 
   existing in other dimensions.  Perhaps this is Tenelorn, or, 
   rather, all the versions of Tanelorn there have ever been.  For 
   Tanelorn exists in many forms, each form depending upon the 
   wishes of those who most desire to find her.

