#16921
{BLUE}The Center of Tanelorn{blue}~
{CYAN}
   At last you approach the likely center of Tanelorn and here is 
   a building which is not ruined.  It stands in a cleared space, all 
   curves and ribbons of metal and glowing tubes.  As you look 
   carefully at the building you can see that it is in fact two 
   buildings... both absolutely identical and joined at various 
   points by curling systems of pipes which might be connecting 
   corridors, though it is difficult to imagine what manner of 
   being might utilize them.  There is no cover to speak of and 
   you can see a point near the ground where a black opening of
   irregular proportions can be discerned.  The buildings pulse 
   and glow and occasionally whisper, but that is all.

