#16922
{BLUE}Inside the Spires{blue}~
{CYAN}
   You and your party are the first to enter here.  You find 
   yourself in a damp, warm passage which curves almost 
   immediately to the right.  It becomes gloomier and brighter in 
   turns.  Sometimes the passages narrow so that it is difficult to 
   squeeze your bodies through, sometimes they widen into what 
   are almost halls.  Most of the time, however, it seems that you 
   are climbing higher into the building.  As you press forward 
   you begin to feel a great sense of uneasiness and you can feel 
   the evil that lurks in the rooms ahead.

