#16923
{BLUE}Gagak's Sanctuary{blue}~
{CYAN}
   This place is octagonal and each of its eight sloping sides are 
   of a different color and each color changes constantly.  
   Occasionally the walls become semitransparent, revealing a 
   complete view of the ruined city far below, and also a view of 
   the twin castle to this one, still connected by tubes and wires.  
   It is the large pool in the center of the room which attracts 
   your attention most.  It seems deep and is full of evil-smelling, 
   viscous stuff.  It bubbles.  Shapes form in it.  Grotesque and 
   strange, beautiful and familiar, the shapes seem always upon 
   the brink of taking a permanent form before falling back into 
   the stuff of the pool.  And the voice is still louder and there is 
   no question that it comes from the pool.    "What? What? Who 
   invades ?!"

