#16924
{BLUE}Agak's Sanctuary{blue}~
{CYAN}
   Agak has awakened too late, but he is awakening at last,
   roused by the dying cries of his sister Gagak, whose body you
   had first invaded and whose intelligence you had first
   overwhelmed, whose eye you now use and whose powers you
   now attempt to utilize.

   But Agak now realizing his danger now begins to draw the
   energy of the universe into himself.  No longer would this be a
   pleasurable ritual shared with his sister.  He must draw at the
   energy of this universe if he were to find the strength to defend
   himself, to gain what he needs to destroy his attackers, the
   slayers of his sister.  Worlds die as Agak drains them.

~
