{MAGENTA}The Lair of the Burning God{magenta}~
{CYAN}
   You press further into the labyrinth, taking a hundred twists and 
   turns in the darkness before you pause again.  You have noticed 
   that it has become warmer.  It feels uncomfortably hot.

   Another turn and you see light ahead.

   You begin to run towards the source of the light.  But it is not 
   daylight, neither is it light from the portal.  This is firelight.... of 
   brands perhaps.  The source of the heat is around the next bend.  
   But the heat has grown greater and your flesh stings as the sweat 
   springs from your pours.

   A great voice suddenly fills the tunnel as you round the last bend 
   and you see the fire leaping not thirty yards distant.

   AAH! AT LAST!

