   an endless city of twisted spires reaching in no particular direction. 
   The diversity of what you see here is staggering.  There is a
   multitude of colors raging about the sky and you can see the dark
   foreboding rainbow of color that heralds the coming storm.

   There is a figure before you, however.  He is tall and regal, and
   utterly evil.  You can see in his beautiful porcelain features
   strength and great power.  He is Arioch, Lord of Chaos!  And the
   fear begins to set in ..... 

